==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Impartible
<hw>Im*part"i*ble</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>im-</ets> not +
<ets>partible</ets>: cf. F. <ets>impartible</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not
partible; not subject to partition; indivisible; <as>as, an
<ex>impartible</ex> estate</as>.</def> <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

